   <text:p text:style-name="P17"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P17">First published <text:span text:style-name="T4">in </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">2026 </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T5">by me (Vladimir Tomasovitch Herdman (Vova))</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P17"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P17">PRINTED… SOMEWHERE, I THINK. AMAZON WASN’T REALLY ALL THAT CLEAR, BUT THEY’RE PRINTING FACILITIES ARE GENERALLY NEAR TO WHERE YOU BUY THIS MATERIAL, SO GOOD LUCK <text:span text:style-name="T4">FIGURING IT OUT</text:span>. IF I’M NOT WRONG, IT SHOULD SAY SOMEWHERE <text:span text:style-name="T4">ON THIS BOOK WHERE</text:span> WAS PRINTED. THOUGH I DON’T REALLY MIND <text:span text:style-name="T4">WHERE</text:span>, AS THIS WAS FREE FROM MY END, <text:span text:style-name="T4">THIS WAS FOR WHOM IT MAY CONCERN</text:span>.</text:p>
