     <text:p text:style-name="P29"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#__RefHeading___Toc784_3676532460" office:name="What Have I Done" text:style-name="Index_20_Link" text:visited-style-name="Index_20_Link">What Have I Done<text:tab/>16</text:a></text:p>
     <text:p text:style-name="P29"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#__RefHeading___Toc1327_3007704144" office:name="Clean Up The Mess" text:style-name="Index_20_Link" text:visited-style-name="Index_20_Link">Clean Up The Mess<text:tab/>17</text:a></text:p>
     <text:p text:style-name="P29"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#__RefHeading___Toc1325_3007704144" office:name="Guilt Comes For Us All" text:style-name="Index_20_Link" text:visited-style-name="Index_20_Link">Guilt Comes For Us All<text:tab/>18</text:a></text:p>
     <text:p text:style-name="P29"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#__RefHeading___Toc1323_3007704144" office:name="Must I Grow Forever" text:style-name="Index_20_Link" text:visited-style-name="Index_20_Link">Must I Grow Forever<text:tab/>19</text:a></text:p>
     <text:p text:style-name="P29"><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#__RefHeading___Toc8146_1175081228" office:name="Remember back in the August of ‘24 when we met face-to-face and how It was our first minicamp together as a team and we sat on a couch near each other and I couldn’t build up the courage to speak to you proper, so I just sat and listened and smiled and kept introducing myself to everyone who came by who asked me who I was? I spoke louder near you because I wanted you to hear me, I wanted you to know I was around and that I was someone to talk to, but all I could think about when you got closer was how much funnier I wanted to be around you, how if I was just a little funnier, I’d have everything I ever wanted and more, how if I was a little smarter, I’d always say the right thing and be charming and be desired, and now I’m screaming with gusto at the walls begging for another chance, but memory’s a fickle liar and will tell you everything you never heard. I’m stuck here thinking of what I’d have done different while all you’re asking me now is" text:style-name="Index_20_Link" text:visited-style-name="Index_20_Link">Remember back in the August of ‘24...<text:tab/>20</text:a></text:p>
